rows.label: qst201003_0020
rows.name: Hey! What are you doing over there?!

rows.label: qst201003_0040
rows.name: Hmpf. Come on. Time to go, Seori!

rows.label: qst201003_0080
rows.name:
I'm sorry. It seems I caused too much
of a disturbance.

rows.label: qst201003_0120
rows.name:
We were, as it happens, in battle with the
Core Crystal hunters terrorizing the area.

rows.label: qst201003_0140
rows.name:
Indeed. The culprits whom we were fighting
were two Blades.

rows.label: qst201003_0150
rows.name:
It's likely that they'll have others conspiring with
them, Drivers included.

rows.label: qst201003_0160
rows.name:
We'd certainly appreciate the army's
assistance in this matter...

rows.label: qst201003_0170
rows.name:
But could I first ask you to report the
details to your superior?

rows.label: qst201003_0190
rows.name: All right, shall we head over to Torigo Relay Base?
